tury. In their quite different ways, these are all classics of that Western drama which is part of our immediate heritage.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aProducteurs et metteurs en scène de théâtrexBiographiesxBiography. 0aTheaterxProduction and direction. 0aTheatrical producers and directorsvBiography. 0aTheatrical producers and directorsxBiography. 0aThéâtrexProduction et mise en scène. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Film & Video / General.2bisacsh  a20th century.  aanton chekhov.  aauteur.  abertolt brecht.  acinema history.  acinema studies.  acontemporary film.  acontemporary theatre.  aculture.  adirecting plays.  adirecting.  adirector.  adrama.  aelia kazan.  afamous directors.  afilm history.  afilm making.  afilmmaking.  ahistory of cinema.  ahistory of film.  ahistory of theatre.  akonstantin stanislavsky.  amodern film.  amodern plays.  amodern theatre.  amother courage.  apeter brook.  aplays.  aplaywright.  astage director.  astage productions.  astage.  astreetcar named desire.  atheatre directing.  atheatre.  atheatrical.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Package Archive Pre-2000z978311063534840uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052090857440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520908574423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520908574/original  a978-3-11-063534-8  University of California Press Package Archive Pre-2000b2000  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles